%I A394108 #15 Mar 16 2026 21:11:57
%S A394108 1,587,28887,49868,228981,158898939,28848999547,76698999868,
%T A394108 493996893887
%N A394108 Numbers k that set a new record for A007953(k) - A004164(k).
%C A394108 The differences between the digit sum of a(n) and the digit sum of a(n)^3, which is always a multiple of 3, for the first few numbers are 0, 3, 6, 9, 12, 15, 18, 21, 30.
%C A394108 The first occurrence of a difference of 24 is found for k=4599599996787. No example of a difference of 27 or larger than 30 is found for k<10^13.
%H A394108 Johannes F. Morgenbesser, <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/publication/228701893_The_sum_of_digits_of_nc">The sum of digits of floor(n^c)</a>, Acta Arithmetica 148 (2011), 367-393.
%e A394108 49868^3 = 124012611300032, the digit sum of 49868 is 35 while the digit sum of its cube is 26, and 35-26=9.
%p A394108 R:= 1: count:= 1: m:= 0:
%p A394108 for x from 2 while count < 6 do
%p A394108   v:= f(x);
%p A394108   if v > m then m:= v; count:= count+1; R:= R,x; fi
%p A394108 od:
%p A394108 R; # _Robert Israel_, Mar 10 2026
%o A394108 (PARI) x=-1; forstep(a=0,10^13,10,y=sumdigits(a); for(b=1,9,d=y+b-sumdigits((a+b)^3); if(d>x,x=d; print1(a+b, ", "))))
%Y A394108 Cf. A004164, A007953, A064209, A204324.
%K A394108 nonn,base,more,new
%O A394108 1,2
%A A394108 _Martin Raab_, Mar 10 2026
